Available stacks:
  nextjs-fastapi-pg    Next.js + FastAPI + PostgreSQL
  spring-vue-mssql     Spring Boot + Vue.js + MSSQL
  react-native-expo    React Native + Expo
  django-react-pg      Django + React + PostgreSQL
`)
}
